        <scopecontent id="ref2">
            <head>Scope and Contents</head>
            <p>Twenty-five VHS videocassettes of opera taped from the Great Performances television series, primarily of the Metropolitan Opera and largely of works by Mozart, Verdi, and Wagner. All were recorded off-air by Hugh Fowell.</p>
        </scopecontent>
